{
  "stem": "17135.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 328.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, he invited us even to meet with his in-laws-- there was a-- a world exposition in Paris at the time, in 1936-- to go there, and to-- to do the details.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My mother said, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "With six children, I'm not going to move.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I'm not going to move.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I stay, and I still believe that God will not permit this to happen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Although he's-- he's predicting and threatening, Hitler is just, you know, a lot of noise.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That's all.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "After the Kristallnacht, she knew that she was wrong, but that was too late.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "By then it was impossible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "All the nations in the world closed their doors.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There was the famous Evian Conference where the United States and other nations promised to take in Jewish refugees, but nothing came out of it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was very, very difficult.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Some got out, but-- but most got stuck.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that is-- and then we lived, so to speak, in limbo until the war broke out on September the 1st.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then a few days later the Gestapo came, and they arrested all the male-- all the male Jews-- foreign Jews.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The German Jews they arrested on Kristallnacht, but the Polish Jews were not arrested then.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Polish Jews were arrested when the war with Poland broke out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "On Nove-- September the 9th-- the war broke out on September the 1st-- they came and took us-- my-- my father, my brother, myself.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Thank God, my older brother, I told you-- oh.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What I forgot to tell you is when my two brothers were in Poland, through the intervention of the Gestapo-- my mother bribed some of the Gestapo people-- they allowed him to come back for the purpose of emigrating.",
      "word_count": 39
    }
  ],
